3 will it be frost in the next two_days ?	the next two_days will be frost , one will be frost with a low of 20f and a high of 40f and the other will be raining , low of 20f with a high of 40f
4 thanks	not a problem

3 for the whole week , please !	the weather next_few_days for grand_rapids is going to be a series of ups and downs from overcast on friday to a frost on thursday and to snow on sunday the highs are forecast to be near 100f with lows near 20f
4 thank you so much for the information	you are welcome have a good day

3 for the whole week , please !	the weather next_few_days for seattle is going to be a series of ups and downs from warm on monday to a frost on thursday and to raining on friday the highs are forecast to be near 80f with lows near 20f
4 thank you so much for the information	you are welcome have a good day
